I had similar problems, partly caused by someone adding the wrong urls to log out (I think they missed the https or something)

But still had the needs a refresh issue which I solved with this line of code on the logout template, not ideal but it worked…

```{% if request_contact.is_logged_in %}
&lt;script&gt;
	location.reload();
&lt;/script&gt;
{% endif %}```
